{"tid":1106592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市熾熱】第一城兩房呎價破2萬   逼去年高峰價","createTime":"2019-04-14T16:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T17:39:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad3b4bec29291c12cc20873e00e394b25f69d98","tid":1106592,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20190414/s00011/0d7487c5a79147841ebd029bad28dd96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20190414%2Fs00011%2F0d7487c5a79147841ebd029bad28dd96.jpg&h=eb3d7b0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「長腳蟹」呂慧儀近年罕有以水著示人，今日在社交網上載一張穿上三點式泳衣，並躺在浮牀上的照片，大騷火辣身材。原來呂慧儀為《開心速遞》拍攝，「朱凌凌」吳偉豪就西裝look在旁保護，呂慧儀難得在鏡頭前性感，於是在網上叫大家下星期捧她場。<br />\n<br />\n呂慧儀留言：「下星期的開心速遞，看不看，告訴我。#型到入血 #型 #朱凌凌 #零零豬 #索 #熊若水 #媽呢空 #紅藥水 #水著水著 #愛回家之開心速遞 #水著與套裝 #搞乜鬼 #泳池邊 #危險 #早晨 #醒神 #記得捧場」<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）"},{"pid":"ba5987e3943f4a7bf1c4ad69411d065231f2dcfd","tid":1106592,"uid":16061,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"屌 今次離譜左啲喎 成篇文都唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07663c536ac1f04fc3fde857cfb2fba9e37dbe1b","tid":1106592,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba5987e3943f4a7bf1c4ad69411d065231f2dcfd","tid":1106592,"uid":16061,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"屌 今次離譜左啲喎 成篇文都唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"SORRY, 係我錯！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190414/s00009/096fbf04b45fe7e626c1179068c20428.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190414%2Fs00009%2F096fbf04b45fe7e626c1179068c20428.jpg&h=f9eb8251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190414/s00009/09716664f173b053b24c960117f5e481.jpg\" data-thumbn